WEBVTT

00:00.734 --> 00:02.568
♪

00:02.570 --> 00:07.272
Another few times before
you try it on your own.

00:07.274 --> 00:09.541
Nope. Ready to give
it a shot!

00:10.744 --> 00:12.044
Ok then.

00:14.614 --> 00:19.518
<i>(grunt)</i>

00:19.520 --> 00:21.153
Can't seem to...

00:21.155 --> 00:26.158
<i>(grunts)</i>

00:27.227 --> 00:28.694
<i>(thud)</i>

00:28.696 --> 00:31.230
Agh! I think I threw
my neck out.

00:31.232 --> 00:36.035
A little more magic practice and
lifting brooms'll be a cinch.

00:36.037 --> 00:38.537
That thing weighs a ton.

00:38.539 --> 00:40.606
Hey, has anypony
here seen my--?

00:40.608 --> 00:42.141
Oh. There it is.

00:42.143 --> 00:46.145
<i>♪ (whistling)</i>

00:46.147 --> 00:49.081
Hmph. I'll never get my
cutie mark for this.

00:49.083 --> 00:52.117
But I'm happy to keep
helping you learn

00:52.119 --> 00:54.420
Just for the fun of
it as long you like.

00:54.422 --> 00:55.387
<i>♪ (whistling)</i>

00:55.389 --> 00:59.058
Hey, who's gonna
clean up this mess?

00:59.060 --> 01:03.228
These are the carefully
arranged pieces of a unicycle

01:03.230 --> 01:05.597
I took apart and will be
putting back together

01:05.599 --> 01:07.699
As soon as twilight
shows me how.

01:09.069 --> 01:12.271
Scootaloo, I already told
you I won't show you how.

01:12.273 --> 01:13.705
But I'll help you
find the instructions

01:13.707 --> 01:15.407
So you can figure
it out yourself.

01:15.409 --> 01:18.277
Blech, I hate research.

01:18.279 --> 01:20.245
To your left, third
shelf from the bottom.

01:20.247 --> 01:21.713
You'll find it in no time.

01:21.715 --> 01:23.549
Thanks so much for
helping us all learn

01:23.551 --> 01:28.821
Always glad to pass on my love
of learning for learning's sake.

01:28.823 --> 01:32.758
Only I'm afraid I'll never get
the hang of this potion-making.

01:32.760 --> 01:34.660
Did you follow the magic
plant-growing formula

01:34.662 --> 01:36.128
I gave you?

01:36.130 --> 01:38.764
Well, uh more or less.

01:40.600 --> 01:42.601
Well, let's try it out
on this apple seedling

01:42.603 --> 01:44.536
<i>And see how we do.</i>

01:44.538 --> 01:47.172
Ooh, I hope this works!

01:52.645 --> 01:53.846
<i>(poof)</i>

01:53.848 --> 01:55.581
<i>(coughing)</i>

01:59.419 --> 02:04.189
<i>(coughing)</i>

02:04.191 --> 02:05.824
<i>(gasping)</i>

02:05.826 --> 02:08.227
<i>(giggles)</i>

02:08.229 --> 02:10.529
Laying it on a little
thick there, aren't we, pal?

02:14.534 --> 02:18.637
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

02:18.639 --> 02:20.205
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

02:20.207 --> 02:23.308
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

02:23.310 --> 02:25.477
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

02:25.479 --> 02:29.615
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

02:29.617 --> 02:30.716
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

02:30.718 --> 02:36.188
<i>♪ it's an easy feat</i>

02:36.190 --> 02:38.323
<i>♪ and magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete ♪</i>

02:38.325 --> 02:40.325
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

02:40.327 --> 02:43.262
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

02:43.264 --> 02:45.898
♪

02:50.203 --> 02:56.808
♪

02:56.810 --> 02:59.478
<i>Diamond tiara: Yoo</i>
<i>hoo! Gather round!</i>

02:59.480 --> 03:01.213
It's time!

03:01.215 --> 03:05.651
<i>(excited curious chatter)</i>

03:05.653 --> 03:08.353
As you all know, I had
promised to put on an amazing

03:08.355 --> 03:12.457
First-time-ever acrobatic
display for you all today.

03:12.459 --> 03:15.761
<i>(cheers)</i>

03:15.763 --> 03:17.963
I know. It's so exciting.

03:17.965 --> 03:19.631
But I'm tired.

03:19.633 --> 03:22.734
<i>(disappointed sighs)</i>

03:22.736 --> 03:25.637
But I did not wish
to disappoint you all,

03:25.639 --> 03:29.441
So I brought my butler
randolph to do them for me.

03:29.443 --> 03:34.846
♪

03:34.848 --> 03:36.381
<i>(thud)</i>

03:37.417 --> 03:39.851
<i>(cheers)</i>

03:39.853 --> 03:42.821
That was amazing,
diamond tiara.

03:42.823 --> 03:46.258
I know. I don't
know how I do it.

03:46.260 --> 03:48.527
I can't believe she
gets so much attention

03:48.529 --> 03:51.330
Without even really
doing anything.

03:51.332 --> 03:53.765
She's using somepony
else to build herself up.

03:53.767 --> 03:56.468
And without even putting in the
effort to learn her own skills

03:56.470 --> 03:59.338
Hey, come to think of it,

03:59.340 --> 04:04.409
Twilight's teaching us, we could
be the big shots around here

04:04.411 --> 04:06.712
For a change. Hmm...

04:09.249 --> 04:10.449
Check this out.

04:12.719 --> 04:13.785
And check this out.

04:15.255 --> 04:16.588
<i>(pop)</i>

04:16.590 --> 04:18.257
<i>(impressed chatter)</i>

04:18.259 --> 04:19.758
<i>And check this out.</i>

04:19.760 --> 04:21.627
Whoa!

04:21.629 --> 04:23.495
Hey! Put me down!

04:23.497 --> 04:28.333
<i>(giggling)</i>

04:28.335 --> 04:30.369
Hey, can't you
hear me?

04:30.371 --> 04:34.473
I was asking if your sister
rarity will be taking you

04:34.475 --> 04:36.908
To manehattan anytime soon.

04:36.910 --> 04:39.611
Because if she is, maybe
you can meet up with us

04:39.613 --> 04:42.714
While we hang out with a
bunch of famous celebrities.

04:42.716 --> 04:44.316
Cool!

04:44.318 --> 04:47.653
Wow, that's pretty
nice of you guys.

04:47.655 --> 04:49.821
Actually, my sister
hasn't offered to take me

04:49.823 --> 04:51.690
To manehattan anytime soon.

04:52.625 --> 04:54.593
Yeah, we figured.

04:54.595 --> 04:56.728
Bump. Bump. Sugarlump. Rump.

04:56.730 --> 04:58.430
<i>(mean giggles)</i>

04:58.432 --> 05:02.401
Oh yeah? Well, I don't have to
go all the way to manehattan

05:02.403 --> 05:04.536
To hang out with the famous
and super-cool ponies.

05:04.538 --> 05:07.372
Me and my friends hang out with
princess twilight all the time!

05:12.512 --> 05:15.414
Did you say
"princess twilight?"

05:15.416 --> 05:17.015
You hang out with
her all the time?

05:17.017 --> 05:18.583
For real?

05:18.585 --> 05:20.519
More like just once a week.

05:20.521 --> 05:22.888
She helps us learn
cool new stuff to do.

05:22.890 --> 05:25.824
That we actually do.
Ourselves!

05:25.826 --> 05:28.927
♪

05:28.929 --> 05:31.563
You must bring me
along next time you go!

05:31.565 --> 05:35.767
<i>Tiara: I mean we used to see</i>
<i>her around town all the time.</i>

05:35.769 --> 05:42.374
But now she's a princess, which
makes her totally awesome.

05:42.376 --> 05:44.343
Plus she has wings.

05:44.345 --> 05:46.011
And she's an alicorn.

05:46.013 --> 05:46.945
So can I?

05:46.947 --> 05:48.547
Go?

05:49.616 --> 05:53.085
Won't you two excuse
us for a moment?

05:55.421 --> 05:57.089
We should totally say yes.

05:57.091 --> 05:58.757
This is a golden opportunity!

05:58.759 --> 06:02.427
I don't want them laughing at
us while I'm mixin' potions

06:02.429 --> 06:05.030
And accidentally sendin'
plants into choking fits!

06:05.032 --> 06:07.833
They'll have to
learn something, too.

06:10.069 --> 06:12.938
And they won't be able to laugh
at us when they're so busy

06:12.940 --> 06:14.806
Trying to learn
stuff of their own.

06:14.808 --> 06:17.709
I must admit it's kinda fun
to see them working hard

06:17.711 --> 06:19.845
To get on our good
side for a change

06:24.150 --> 06:26.551
<i>Diamond tiara: Oh my gosh, a</i>
<i>princess lives in there.</i>

06:26.553 --> 06:28.587
And I'm about to go
inside and see her!

06:28.589 --> 06:30.956
I can't even tell
you how excited I am!

06:30.958 --> 06:32.457
I can't either!

06:34.728 --> 06:38.029
Now remember, twilight takes
this time out with us

06:38.031 --> 06:39.631
So we can learn stuff.

06:39.633 --> 06:41.433
Hey there, guys!
Come on in.

06:41.435 --> 06:42.734
<i>(swooning screams)</i>

06:42.736 --> 06:45.103
Princess twilight!

06:45.105 --> 06:46.972
Oh! It's really her!

06:46.974 --> 06:48.940
Oh my gosh! I don't believe it!

06:49.942 --> 06:52.411
Oh, and uh, you
brought guests.

06:52.413 --> 06:57.449
Princess twilight, it is such
a thrill and honor to be here,

06:57.451 --> 06:58.683
You have no idea.

06:58.685 --> 07:01.186
Oh my gosh, who dyes your tail?

07:01.188 --> 07:03.021
I so have to
get that done.

07:03.023 --> 07:04.756
Actually, it's not dyed.

07:04.758 --> 07:07.793
<i>Diamond tiara: (gasp) are</i>
<i>those books in there?</i>

07:07.795 --> 07:09.828
What a bold design choice.

07:09.830 --> 07:12.197
You should so do that, di.

07:12.199 --> 07:14.466
I know, right?

07:14.468 --> 07:18.170
Listen. I'm all for helping
as many ponies as I can,

07:18.172 --> 07:19.971
But maybe we should keep
these weekly visits

07:19.973 --> 07:21.706
Just between us, hm?

07:25.478 --> 07:28.513
Ok, which one of you
wants to practice first?

07:28.515 --> 07:29.981
Shouldn't they go first?

07:29.983 --> 07:34.453
No silly, I set up twilight
time especially for you.

07:34.455 --> 07:35.887
Applebloom, go ahead.

07:35.889 --> 07:37.823
Let's see how your plant
potions are coming.

07:45.031 --> 07:46.865
I can't believe I
let you talk us

07:46.867 --> 07:48.567
Into bringing
guests yesterday.

07:48.569 --> 07:51.102
I didn't hear them laugh
at us once, applebloom.

07:51.104 --> 07:52.971
Because they laughed
on the inside.

07:52.973 --> 07:55.974
We won't make that
same mistake again.

07:56.743 --> 08:00.679
Look who showed up
to make fun of us.

08:00.681 --> 08:03.715
So much for learning
skills to be big shots.

08:03.717 --> 08:05.250
Hey, guess what!

08:05.252 --> 08:09.120
I told everyone about your
special twilight time!

08:09.122 --> 08:11.990
Oh no, here it comes.

08:11.992 --> 08:14.059
And they all want in!

08:14.061 --> 08:20.031
Twilight time! Twilight time!
(continues)

08:20.033 --> 08:23.635
Thanks to me, you three are
now the hottest thing around.

08:23.637 --> 08:25.136
You're welcome.

08:25.138 --> 08:26.872
Twilight time! Twilight time!
Twilight time!

08:26.874 --> 08:28.206
Uh oh.

08:30.810 --> 08:34.012
Twilight time! Twilight time!

08:34.014 --> 08:36.882
Wow! All these ponies really
want to meet twilight

08:36.884 --> 08:38.817
That badly?

08:38.819 --> 08:41.520
We love you, cutie
mark crusaders!

08:41.522 --> 08:45.257
<i>(cheers)</i>

08:45.259 --> 08:47.859
<i>Diamond tiara: Now</i>
<i>now, everypony.</i>

08:47.861 --> 08:50.862
Demanding time with a
princess as an unruly mob

08:50.864 --> 08:52.964
Simply won't do.

08:52.966 --> 08:55.567
Might I suggest you get
organized through us,

08:55.569 --> 08:59.905
The cutie mark crusaders'
nearest and dearest friends?

08:59.907 --> 09:02.240
Everypony get in line.

09:02.242 --> 09:04.042
No pushing. No pushing!

09:04.044 --> 09:06.545
<i>(excited shouts)</i>

09:06.547 --> 09:08.113
What a mess.

09:08.115 --> 09:13.051
Don't you see? We're really
and truly and certifiably

09:13.053 --> 09:15.787
The biggest of the bigshots
in school right now!

09:15.789 --> 09:18.723
They all think
we're the greatest

09:18.725 --> 09:24.796
Ponyville's newest and biggest
celebrity: Princess twilight.

09:24.798 --> 09:27.766
We just said like two seconds
ago that inviting two ponies

09:27.768 --> 09:30.168
To twilight time
was a big mistake!

09:30.170 --> 09:32.804
<i>And now we're supposed to</i>
<i>bring the whole class?</i>

09:32.806 --> 09:33.838
Relax.

09:33.840 --> 09:34.906
I got this.

09:38.277 --> 09:40.879
I don't like this,
sweetie belle.

09:40.881 --> 09:43.982
You said not to invite them
to twilight time and I didn't,

09:43.984 --> 09:45.150
So what's the problem?

09:45.152 --> 09:47.085
This feels like a trick.

09:47.087 --> 09:49.688
What's tricky about inviting
twilight out for a meal

09:49.690 --> 09:52.357
Thanking her for all the nice
things she's done for us?

09:52.359 --> 09:55.060
Seems like the least
we can do for the princess.

09:55.062 --> 09:56.895
Did someone say princess?

10:03.202 --> 10:05.804
When I told you when you could
come eyeball the princess

10:05.806 --> 10:09.274
I said only two or
three of you, tops.

10:09.276 --> 10:11.943
<i>All: Oops.</i>

10:11.945 --> 10:13.244
She's coming!

10:13.246 --> 10:15.380
Ok, but stay out of sight.

10:15.382 --> 10:17.382
As you wish, sweetie belle.

10:17.384 --> 10:19.217
Yes. As I wish.

10:20.252 --> 10:21.653
<i>(chewing)</i>

10:21.655 --> 10:25.323
Mmmm. Mmm.

10:25.325 --> 10:27.392
I didn't realize
how hungry I was.

10:27.394 --> 10:29.961
I'm so glad you asked
me to join you here today.

10:29.963 --> 10:30.929
<i>(swallows)</i>

10:30.931 --> 10:32.063
I'm so honored.

10:33.966 --> 10:35.000
<i>(chomp)</i>

10:35.836 --> 10:39.671
When you first asked me to
help you develop new skills,

10:39.673 --> 10:42.107
I thought: Working with young
students so devoted to the joy

10:42.109 --> 10:44.075
Of learning purely
for its own sake?

10:44.077 --> 10:48.079
You all remind me of
myself when I was your age.

10:48.081 --> 10:51.082
<i>(chewing)</i>

10:51.084 --> 10:53.785
Yes, well, we feel
the same way.

10:53.787 --> 10:55.954
That's why we invited you here.

10:55.956 --> 10:57.856
Because of our love
of learning.

10:58.824 --> 10:59.991
<i>(slurp)</i>

10:59.993 --> 11:04.329
Haven't seen you here in,
like, forever-and-a-half!

11:04.331 --> 11:08.833
I've been so busy I forgot how
delicious everything is here.

11:08.835 --> 11:10.335
Totally!

11:10.337 --> 11:12.137
Hey, what's going on
out there?

11:14.407 --> 11:15.974
Oh, never mind. They're gone.

11:17.109 --> 11:17.976
They're back!

11:17.978 --> 11:20.045
Never mind. They're gone.

11:20.047 --> 11:21.813
<i>♪ la la la la la.</i>

11:22.848 --> 11:31.956
<i>(camera shutters clicking)</i>

11:31.958 --> 11:34.192
Knock it off!

11:34.194 --> 11:36.728
What in the world is
going on out--?

11:36.730 --> 11:37.929
<i>(gasp)</i>

11:41.300 --> 11:43.268
What was all this?

11:43.270 --> 11:45.170
And this?

11:45.172 --> 11:49.040
When I don't smile in
a picture, I look sad.

11:49.042 --> 11:51.443
Oh, we're gonna
look sad all right.

11:53.045 --> 11:53.978
<i>(door closes)</i>

11:53.980 --> 11:55.080
<i>(gasp)</i>

11:55.082 --> 11:59.117
<i>(birds chirping)</i>

11:59.119 --> 12:01.853
Uh, can I help you?

12:01.855 --> 12:07.025
<i>(excited screams)</i>

12:07.027 --> 12:08.326
Get my picture
with her!

12:08.328 --> 12:09.427
Me first!

12:09.429 --> 12:11.429
Hey, get out of the shot!

12:11.431 --> 12:15.467
Twilight's gonna be
so ticked at us.

12:15.469 --> 12:18.203
I told you this was
a terrible idea.

12:18.205 --> 12:21.506
You seriously all
want my autograph?

12:21.508 --> 12:24.409
Ok, I'll sign just a
couple more for you,

12:24.411 --> 12:27.145
But then I really must get
back to my little friends.

12:30.183 --> 12:35.820
Wow, to think I've been to the
hay burger so many times

12:35.822 --> 12:38.523
Never knowing it was the
regular hangout for a princess!

12:38.525 --> 12:40.892
This isn't my regular hang out.

12:40.894 --> 12:43.094
I'm only here to be with them.

12:43.096 --> 12:45.463
You mean, princess
twilight decides

12:45.465 --> 12:49.467
Where it's cool to go
based on where they go?

12:49.469 --> 12:51.269
Wha - ?

12:51.271 --> 12:52.971
Thanks guys. This was fun.

12:54.440 --> 12:56.007
See you around.

12:57.143 --> 12:59.544
<i>(excited chatter)</i>

12:59.546 --> 13:01.546
I'm opening a new
lemonade stand.

13:01.548 --> 13:03.414
Won't you come to the
grand opening?

13:05.484 --> 13:07.519
I'll give you free
lemonade for a week.

13:09.555 --> 13:13.224
Relax. I know exactly
how to handle this.

13:14.426 --> 13:15.460
<i>(snip)</i>

13:15.462 --> 13:17.328
<i>(cheers)</i>

13:17.330 --> 13:19.164
Yippee! Lemonade!

13:19.166 --> 13:23.101
♪

13:23.103 --> 13:24.102
More lemonade?

13:24.104 --> 13:25.303
Don't mind if I do.

13:25.305 --> 13:30.942
♪

13:30.944 --> 13:34.045
It's an honor to do
you the favor.

13:35.314 --> 13:37.849
Wow, so bright I can see myself.

13:37.851 --> 13:39.584
And so can I.

13:39.586 --> 13:42.220
Nice job
bedazzling my bow.

13:42.222 --> 13:45.924
Your gratitude is
thanks enough.

13:48.494 --> 13:51.596
You three must come
to my pool party.

13:51.598 --> 13:53.932
It'll be much
cooler than this.

13:55.334 --> 13:58.169
Look who's inviting
who to her fancy house.

13:58.171 --> 14:01.406
I believe we have arrived,
cutie mark crusaders.

14:01.408 --> 14:02.540
Yeah!

14:04.210 --> 14:06.277
<i>(splash)</i>

14:06.279 --> 14:11.216
Wow, this is nice, but
there's no one else here.

14:11.218 --> 14:14.018
Why is this party
cooler exactly?

14:14.020 --> 14:17.322
Because of all the
ponies we're keeping out.

14:21.327 --> 14:23.895
This has been great,
but we have to go.

14:24.530 --> 14:26.030
It's twilight time.

14:27.333 --> 14:30.034
So we're coming
too, right?

14:30.036 --> 14:31.603
Um...

14:31.605 --> 14:33.504
Actually no.

14:34.506 --> 14:37.208
We didn't have a chance
to ask twilight, so...

14:37.210 --> 14:40.945
Really? After all the
favors we did for you?

14:40.947 --> 14:44.249
After all the favors
they did for you?

14:44.251 --> 14:47.252
Twilight time! Twilight time!

14:47.254 --> 14:49.587
Twilight time! Twilight time!

14:49.589 --> 14:55.627
<i>(chanting continues)</i>

14:55.629 --> 14:58.630
Ok. I know exactly
how to handle this.

14:58.632 --> 15:00.031
Run!

15:02.635 --> 15:08.106
Twilight time! Twilight time!

15:08.108 --> 15:13.077
<i>(struggling grunts)</i>

15:13.079 --> 15:15.513
We've got to beat them to
twilight's so we can explain.

15:15.515 --> 15:17.415
This way. I know a short cut.

15:18.484 --> 15:20.551
Twilight time! Twilight time!

15:20.553 --> 15:22.320
Then we run...Like the wind!

15:26.625 --> 15:28.393
<i>(gasping as she speaks)</i>

15:28.395 --> 15:31.195
We made it! Quick, knock on--

15:31.197 --> 15:32.964
<i>(tire screech)</i>

15:32.966 --> 15:39.971
<i>♪ (scary)</i>

15:39.973 --> 15:41.539
<i>(knock knock)</i>

15:41.541 --> 15:42.640
<i>(door opens)</i>

15:43.977 --> 15:48.346
We know you said we should
just keep twilight time to us.

15:48.348 --> 15:50.682
We didn't mean for so many
other ponies to be here.

15:50.684 --> 15:52.183
Honest!

15:53.119 --> 16:01.392
But if you want to share your
time with others, that's fine.

16:01.394 --> 16:04.028
So you're not mad?

16:04.030 --> 16:05.263
Of course not.

16:05.265 --> 16:06.731
Come on in, everypony.

16:06.733 --> 16:08.633
Spike made nachos.

16:08.635 --> 16:12.570
<i>(happy chatter)</i>

16:12.572 --> 16:14.505
Turns out we'll need
some more than that.

16:16.408 --> 16:17.475
<i>(sigh)</i>

16:19.044 --> 16:23.047
<i>(chatter)</i>

16:23.049 --> 16:26.484
Before we start, we should
maybe get a bit more organized.

16:26.486 --> 16:29.053
Ponies interested in
magic in this corner.

16:29.055 --> 16:31.656
Ponies who want to learn
potions over here.

16:31.658 --> 16:33.691
Bookworm
ponies over there.

16:36.029 --> 16:40.131
Looks like everything's
working out just fine.

16:40.133 --> 16:43.434
And I was so afraid twilight
would be disappointed in us.

16:43.436 --> 16:46.270
Told you I knew exactly
how to handle all this.

16:46.272 --> 16:48.306
Thanks to all of you
for taking time out

16:48.308 --> 16:50.141
To come learn new things.

16:50.143 --> 16:52.377
Thank  <i>you</i> , princess!

16:52.379 --> 16:53.678
We love you, princess!

16:53.680 --> 16:56.214
<i>(cheers)</i>

16:56.216 --> 16:58.549
Ok, ok, let's settle down.

16:58.551 --> 17:02.020
If you want to thank anypony,
thank the cutie mark crusaders

17:02.022 --> 17:04.722
<i>For so generously</i>
<i>sharing this time.</i>

17:04.724 --> 17:08.526
We just felt it was
the right thing to do.

17:08.528 --> 17:09.427
Hmph.

17:09.429 --> 17:11.162
What a laugh.

17:11.164 --> 17:12.730
Let's begin over here.

17:12.732 --> 17:15.233
And what would you like
to learn, little one?

17:15.235 --> 17:18.669
I want to learn how to
become a cutie mark crusader.

17:18.671 --> 17:22.673
And why do you want to become
a cutie mark crusader so badly?

17:22.675 --> 17:25.510
Because then I could get all my
classmates to do me favors

17:25.512 --> 17:28.513
And stuff because I'm friends
with a famous princess.

17:32.184 --> 17:34.152
Hoo boy.

17:34.154 --> 17:38.589
We wanted our time together
just as a way to be with you

17:38.591 --> 17:39.524
And learn new things.

17:39.526 --> 17:41.392
Really and truly.

17:41.394 --> 17:42.493
Prove it.

17:42.495 --> 17:46.297
If it's true, then I'm sure
you've all been practicing

17:46.299 --> 17:48.266
Your skills over the past week.

17:48.268 --> 17:50.268
Show me how much better you got.

17:51.503 --> 17:56.107
Uh well, uh, we can't.

17:56.109 --> 17:59.243
We kind of rushed over and
forgot to bring our stuff.

17:59.245 --> 18:00.812
Hmm. I see.

18:01.848 --> 18:05.183
Hey everypony, you're in luck.

18:05.185 --> 18:10.855
Get ready, 'cause we,
the cutie mark crusaders,

18:10.857 --> 18:13.257
Are about to lay on
you the amazing skills

18:13.259 --> 18:15.359
We learned in twilight time!

18:15.361 --> 18:20.431
<i>(curious chatter)</i>

18:20.433 --> 18:23.868
Unfortunately, since we don't
have scootaloo's unicycle parts,

18:23.870 --> 18:25.570
She'll take apart and
put back together

18:25.572 --> 18:27.572
One of the scooters
from outside.

18:27.574 --> 18:30.141
Hey, that's my scooter!

18:30.143 --> 18:31.642
You got us into this mess, kid.

18:31.644 --> 18:33.411
Might wanna roll with us.

18:33.413 --> 18:39.550
<i>So she'll just grab an</i>
<i>apple from the kitchen.</i>

18:39.552 --> 18:44.222
And I will begin by using
my magic to lift this broom.

18:44.224 --> 18:54.165
♪

18:54.167 --> 18:55.233
<i>(clink clink)</i>

18:55.235 --> 18:56.400
<i>(poof)</i>

18:56.402 --> 19:00.438
♪

19:00.440 --> 19:01.706
<i>♪ ta da!</i>

19:01.708 --> 19:04.142
Become a tree!

19:04.144 --> 19:05.309
Rise!

19:07.279 --> 19:08.412
<i>(thud)</i>

19:08.414 --> 19:09.647
<i>(clatter)</i>

19:14.153 --> 19:16.154
<i>(explosion)</i>

19:16.156 --> 19:19.390
That didn't turn out
quite how I had hoped.

19:19.392 --> 19:22.160
Looks like twilight
time is over.

19:22.162 --> 19:25.730
And look who's not the
princess' entourage anymore.

19:25.732 --> 19:27.932
<i>All: Oooooh!</i>

19:27.934 --> 19:30.801
Guess they didn't come
here to learn after all.

19:30.803 --> 19:33.738
Well, neither did any of you.

19:33.740 --> 19:35.740
Awwwww.

19:38.677 --> 19:40.811
We're really sorry, twilight.

19:40.813 --> 19:42.613
We made a huge mistake.

19:42.615 --> 19:44.615
And we really and truly
did enjoy learning

19:44.617 --> 19:49.587
Guess we'll just have to keep
on doing it without you now.

19:49.589 --> 19:51.455
Thanks, twilight.

19:52.925 --> 19:54.225
<i>(poof)</i>

19:57.696 --> 19:58.829
Thanks.

19:58.831 --> 20:06.270
♪

20:06.272 --> 20:07.471
Thanks.

20:12.778 --> 20:13.945
Sweetie belle?

20:16.381 --> 20:19.817
Remember a moment ago when you
asked me to "give you a chance?"

20:22.721 --> 20:25.356
<i>(grunts)</i>

20:29.294 --> 20:30.895
Awww, come on!

20:33.265 --> 20:36.000
<i>I guess twilight must not</i>
<i>be so super upset anymore</i>

20:36.002 --> 20:39.403
<i>'cause she's letting us do a</i>
<i>diary entry like our sisters do.</i>

20:39.405 --> 20:41.939
<i>Boy, did we get our</i>
<i>priorities mixed up.</i>

20:41.941 --> 20:45.710
<i>Because we were friends</i>
<i>with someone special.</i>

20:45.712 --> 20:49.280
<i>We almost forgot the real</i>
<i>reason she's special:</i>

20:49.282 --> 20:51.916
<i>Because she's our friend.</i>

20:51.918 --> 20:56.687
<i>But she forgave us and, like</i>
<i>magic, things are good as new.</i>

20:56.689 --> 21:00.424
<i>That's the kind of magic I</i>
<i>really want to get good at...</i>

21:00.426 --> 21:02.760
<i>Now that I'm getting so</i>
<i>good at the other kind.</i>

21:04.596 --> 21:08.332
Wow, all three of you have
made so much progress.

21:08.334 --> 21:09.900
I'm really proud of you!

21:09.902 --> 21:11.469
See you next time.

21:13.272 --> 21:16.007
<i>We're just glad twilight</i>
<i>time is back to normal.</i>

21:16.009 --> 21:19.310
<i>Well? Almost back to normal.</i>

21:19.312 --> 21:21.045
I just hope no one sees us.

21:21.047 --> 21:23.714
Because we're trying to keep
twilight time a secret now?

21:23.716 --> 21:25.916
Or because we
look ridiculous?

21:25.918 --> 21:27.718
A little of both,
actually.

21:29.421 --> 21:30.721
<i>(laughter)</i>
